Package it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.schema

Class Cube

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.schema.Cube
  • public class Cube
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements an OLAP cube, namely a set of dimensions, hierarchies and measures. The methods manipulate or perform checks on the cube's fields.
